node.name: Vertical Blur
node.shortHelp:
A Vertical blur will apply a gausian filter in the y direction.
Radius controls the amount of blur.
node.longHelp:
A Vertical blur will apply a gausian filter in the y direction.
Radius controls the amount of blur.

node.name: Horizontal Blur
node.shortHelp:
A Horizontal blur will apply a gausian filter in the x direction.
Radius controls the amount of blur.
node.longHelp:
A Horizontal blur will apply a gausian filter in the x direction.
Radius controls the amount of blur.

node.name: Colour Correction
node.source: return pow( ( getInput("Input",coords) + getAttribute("Blacks") ) * getAttribute("Whites"), (1.0 / ( 1 + 2 * ( getAttribute("Middles") - 0.5 ) ) ) );
node.shortHelp: A Colour Correction node allows you to correct the black, white and middtones of your image.
node.longHelp: A Colour Correction node allows you to correct the black, white and middtones of your image.
